thread.title: New satellite images show China's growing navy

title: New satellite images show China's growing navy
text:
New satellite images show China's growing navy 5:41am EDT - 02:03 
Dozens of Chinese naval vessels are exercising this week with an aircraft carrier in a large show of force off Hainan Island in the South China Sea, satellite images obtained by Reuters show. Reuters' Greg Torode reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
